support.installation_instructions:
Simply click install.

Once installed, you will need to connect with your Zest account: this is a one-time operation to do with a Zendesk admin profile:

- open any ticket and look at Zest app in the sidebar, or open Zest app from the editor ;

- click on the blue Sign in button ;

- sign into Zest or just create your Zest account if you don’t have one already ;

- then accept the connection between Zest and Zendesk when proposed ;

- done! go back to Zendesk and refresh your browser to see the app now ready.

If you use former Zendesk Chat, please note that you will need to install our addon app named “Screen Recording by Zest - addon for former Zendesk Chat“ to get Zest into Chat.

chat.installation_instructions:
This is an addon to enable Zest for your former Zendesk Chat version (Zopim). If you enabled Zendesk Agent Workspace you don’t need to install this app.

Simply click install.

Once installed, you will need to connect with your Zest account: this is a one-time operation to do with a Zendesk admin profile:

- open any ticket and look at Zest app in a chat sidebar;

- click on the blue Sign in button ;

- sign into Zest or just create your Zest account if you don’t have one already ;

- then accept the connection between Zest and Zendesk when proposed ;

- done! go back to Zendesk and refresh your browser to see the app now ready.
